Texts.Chs: 把^orange;组织培养物^reset;带回^orange;科学前哨站^reset;给^green;我^reset;。
Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Tissue Culture^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

Texts.Chs: 做得很好。作为感谢把这个拿去吧。这是非常少见的，你应该会用到的。
Texts.Eng: You're doing great. As a thanks, take this. It's rare, but it might come in handy some day.

Texts.Chs: ^orange;植物纤维^reset;是分布非常丰富的资源，试着把它放入物质萃取器，然后把一些^orange;组织培养物^reset;带给我吧。
Texts.Eng: ^orange;Plant fibre^reset; is plentiful enough that extracting some for a little ^orange;tissue culture^reset; won't hurt. Bring me some.
